reviews.review_text:
finally an aud not recorded in Bruins Pro Shop Being my first show I've always wanted a decent aud to go with the passable sbd in circulation from this night.The other offering here was far from satisfying.

Thank you for great recording of a fond memory.
3 stars because it's not that strong a show, although a good recording.
Thanks Thanks Ole Uncle John....but...only 3 stars for "a great recording"?  :-) enjoy

Sounds good This building was a tough place to hear live let alone capture it on tape. Yet this recording gets it rite along with few others. Odd to have Jerry be the one to say we are going to take a short break back in a few minutes.

Fond Memory This was not only my first Dead show, but my first concert ever!  It was a great night and for my money a good show.  Maybe not the best they ever did, but they popped my cherry that night and that alone makes this a truly memorable show!  Thanks for posting it!
